<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f5f6f8;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
<td align="center" style="padding:4px">

<table width="420" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="
background:#ffffff;
border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px #000000;
">

<!-- Header -->
<tr>
<td align="center" style="padding:2px;">

<img src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/image3.png" alt="Superfan" style="width:140px;" />

<h1 style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#111827;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;padding-bottom:2px;">
You're Invited!
</h1>

<p style="margin:8px 0 0;font-size:14px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.4">
<strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to become an admin on
<strong>SUPERFAN</strong>
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Invitation Details -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 20px 6px">

<div style="background:#ffffff;padding:14px;font-size:14px;color:#374151">

<strong style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;color:#9ca3af;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:11px;">
Invitation Details
</strong>

<table width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">

<tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;">
<td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;">Invited by:</td>
<td align="right" style="font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-size:13px;">
{{inviterName}}
</td>
</tr>

<tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;">
<td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;">Role:</td>
<td align="right" style="font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-size:13px;">
{{role}}
</td>
</tr>

<tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;">
<td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;">Platform:</td>
<td align="right" style="font-weight:bold;color:#000000;font-size:13px;">
SUPERFAN
</td>
</tr>

</table>
</div>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- Secure Access Link -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 20px 16px">

<div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #000000;border-radius:2px;padding:6px;color:#000000">

<div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1px;color:#000000">
🔒 Secure Access Link
</div>

<p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.5">
Click the button below to accept your admin invitation.
This link is unique to you and will expire in
<strong>{{expiryDays}} days</strong>.
</p>

<!-- Link preview -->
<div style="
background:#f3f4f6;
border-radius:4px;
padding:12px;
font-size:12px;
color:#9ca3af;
word-break:break-all;
margin-bottom:14px;
font-family:monospace;
">
{{inviteUrl}}
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
<a
href="{{inviteUrl}}"
style="
display:block;
background:#000000;
color:#ffffff;
text-decoration:none;
padding:14px;
border-radius:9999px;
font-size:14px;
font-weight:700;
text-align:center
"
>
Accept Admin Invitation
</a>

</div>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- What happens next -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 16px 12px">

<div style="background:#ffffff;padding:14px">

<strong style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;text-transform:uppercase;">
What happens next?
</strong>

<ol style="margin:0;padding-left:0;font-size:12px;color:#000000;line-height:1.6;list-style:none;">

<li style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;width:20px;height:20px;line-height:20px;text-align:center;background:#000;color:#ffffff;border-radius:50%;margin-right:10px;font-weight:bold;font-size:12px;">1</span>
Click the ‘Accept Admin Invitation’ button above
</li>

<li style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;width:20px;height:20px;line-height:20px;text-align:center;background:#000;color:#ffffff;border-radius:50%;margin-right:10px;font-weight:bold;font-size:12px;">2</span>
Review your admin permissions and access level
</li>

<li style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;width:20px;height:20px;line-height:20px;text-align:center;background:#000;color:#ffffff;border-radius:50%;margin-right:10px;font-weight:bold;font-size:12px;">3</span>
Confirm acceptance to activate your admin account
</li>

<li style="display:flex;align-items:center;">
<span style="display:inline-block;width:20px;height:20px;line-height:20px;text-align:center;background:#000;color:#ffffff;border-radius:50%;margin-right:10px;font-weight:bold;font-size:12px;">4</span>
Start managing superfan immediately
</li>

</ol>

</div>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- Security Notice -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 20px 20px">

<div style="
background:#fffbeb;
border:1px solid #fde68a;
border-radius:12px;
padding:12px;
font-size:14px;
color:#92400e;
line-height:1.5
">

⚠️ <strong>Security Notice</strong><br />

This invitation link is unique and secure.
Never share this link with anyone.

If you didn’t expect this invitation or believe it was sent in error,
you can safely ignore it.

</div>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Footer -->
<tr>
<td align="center" style="padding:0px;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af">

<div style="background-color:#f2f4f73c;">

<hr style="border-color:#e5e7eb1a;width:90%;border-width:0.1px;"/>

Need help? Contact us at
<strong style="color:#000000">superfanng@superfan.ng</strong>

<p style="font-size:10px;">
© 2026 superfan. All rights reserved.
</p>

<p style="font-size:10px;">
This invitation will expire on {{expiryDate}}.
</p>

</div>

</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>